  <original-body>A call to utc modifies the object itself.

&lt;code&gt;
&gt;&gt; t = Time.now
=&gt; Thu May 06 16:15:14 +0200 2010
&gt;&gt; t.utc
=&gt; Thu May 06 14:15:14 UTC 2010
&gt;&gt; t
=&gt; Thu May 06 14:15:14 UTC 2010
&lt;/code&gt;

It shouldn't be like that or the method should be called `.utc!`</original-body>
